 <p>Gapat Bot is provided"as is" without any warranty. We are not liable for:</p>
 <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1" style="color:var(--text-muted)">
 <li>Damage or data loss resulting from bot usage</li>
 <li>Downtime or unavailability of service</li>
 <li>AI-generated content that may be inaccurate or inappropriate</li>
 <li>Actions of other users who use the bot</li>
 </ul>
 </section>

 <section>
 <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3" style="color:var(--text-primary)">5. Service Limitations</h2>
 <p>We reserve the right to:</p>
 <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1" style="color:var(--text-muted)">
 <li>Limit bot usage if it exceeds reasonable bounds</li>
 <li>Deny access to servers that violate the terms</li>
 <li>Change or discontinue features at any time with notice</li>
 <li>Update these Terms of Service from time to time</li>
 </ul>
 </section>

 <section>
 <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3" style="color:var(--text-primary)">6. Intellectual Property</h2>
 <p>All rights to Gapat Bot, including code, design, and brand, belong to the developer. You may not use bot assets without written permission.</p>
 </section>

 <section>
 <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3" style="color:var(--text-primary)">7. Termination</h2>
 <p>We reserve the right to terminate access to the bot if these terms are violated. You may stop using the bot at any time by removing it from your Discord server.</p>
 </section>

 <section>
 <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3" style="color:var(--text-primary)">8. Contact</h2>
 <p>For questions or to report violations, contact us through our Discord support server.</p>
 </section>
 </div>
 </div>

 </div>
</body>
</html>
